Survey expression rules:
- radiogroup, dropdown → SINGLE SCALAR value → use equality: {x} = 'value'
- checkbox, tagbox → ARRAY value (multi-select) → NEVER use equality → use contains({x}, 'value') or {x} contains 'value'
- boolean → BOOLEAN value → use true/false logic: {x} = true, not {x}
- number → NUMBER value → use numeric comparison: >, >=, <, <=
- text → STRING value → use string comparison or functions: != '', length({x}) > 0
- panel / static elements → NO VALUE → must not be referenced in expressions
